<i>noun</i>: 초밥 [초밥], 스시 [壽司] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>초밥 [초밥]</dt><br>
<dd>sushi; roll</dd><br>
<dd>식초와 소금으로 간을 하여 작게 뭉친 흰밥에 생선을 얹거나 김, 유부 등으로 싸서 만든 일본 음식.</dd><br>
<dd>A Japanese dish made by placing fish on a small ball of rice seasoned with vinegar and salt, or by wrapping the rice ball with dried laver, fried tofu, etc.</dd><br>
<dt>스시 [壽司]</dt><br>
<dd>sushi</dd><br>
<dd>주로 식초로 간을 한 밥을 작게 뭉쳐 생선, 달걀, 채소 등을 얹거나 싸서 만든 일본 음식.</dd><br>
<dd>A Japanese dish made by lumping boiled rice sprinkled with vinegar into bite-size pieces and placing fish, eggs, vegetables, etc., on top or using them as a wrapping.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>